comments: Replay review of the foul called on Winslow(LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Winslow turns into Harden's (BKN) body and affects his ability to finish near the rim.
Claxton (BKN) legally contests Jackson's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Bledsoe (LAC) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Winslow (LAC) and Durant (BKN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Mann (LAC) is already in Durant's (BKN) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Coffey's (LAC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Bledsoe (LAC) legally contests Durant's (BKN) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Coffey (LAC) and Johnson (BKN) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Harden (BKN) rests his hands on Coffey's (LAC) back and marginal contact occurs as Harden releases away to secure the long rebound.
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Harden (BKN).
Bembry (BKN) commits a take foul on Bledsoe (LAC).
Griffin (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Coffey (LAC) and is firming up when contact occurs.
Winslow (LAC) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Bledsoe (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown (BKN) and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
